<h1>{gt text="Little HTML- School"}</h1>
<br/>
<p>{gt text="This modul work with HTML- Tags. To write a text in a right format, you have to use HTML. Here is a schor overview of the general HTML-Tags."}</p>
</br>
<ol>
	<li><b>{gt text="Title:"}</b> {gt text="There is a hierarchy of titles. You can use highest title by writing '&lt;h1>'Here is my text'&lt;/h1>'. Lower title are created with &lt;h2> and so on."}</li>
	<li><b>{gt text="Text:"}</b> {gt text="To write your text HTML- comformely you have to use a &lt;p> Tag. You use it like this:'&lt;p>My Text&lt;/p>'"}</li>
	<li><b>{gt text="Wordwrap"}</b> {gt text="To get an new Line you have to use this tag: '&lt;br/>'."}</li>
	<li><b>{gt text="Design a text"}</b> {gt text="To design the text, you can use following Tags:"}</li>
	<ol>
		<li><b>{gt text="Bold"}</b> {gt text="To make your text boldly, you use this tag:'&lt;b>Bold Text&lt;/b>'"}</li>
		<li><b>{gt text="Italic"}</b> {gt text="To make your text italicly, you use this tag:'&lt;i>Italic Text&lt;/i>'"}</li>
		<li><b>{gt text="Underline"}</b> {gt text="To unterline your text, you use this tag:'&lt;u>Underlied Text&lt;/u>'"}</li>
	</ol>
	<li><b>{gt text="Structure a text"}</b> {gt text="To structure the text, you can use following Tags:"}</li>
	<ol>
		<li><b>{gt text="List with dots"}</b> {gt text="To create a list with dots you can use this tag:'&lt;ul>&lt;li>Text in list&lt;/li>&lt;/ul>'. To create more then one list entry you use the &lt;li> tags more the one time."}</li>
		<li><b>{gt text="List with numbering"}</b> {gt text="To create a list with numbering you can use this tag:'&lt;ol>&lt;li>Text in list&lt;/li>&lt;/ol>'. To create more then one list entry you use the &lt;li> tags more the one time."}</li>
		<li><b>{gt text="Table"}</b> {gt text="To create a table you can use this tag:'&lt;table>&lt;tr>&lt;th>Title of th column&lt;/th>&lt;td>Text in one cell&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>'. To create more then one row you use the &lt;tr> tags more the one time. To create more then one column you use the &lt;th> / &lt;td> tags more the one time in each row."}</li>
		<li><b>{gt text="Deviding line"}</b> {gt text="To create a deviding line you use this tag: '&lt;hr/>'."}</li>
	</ol>
	<li><b>{gt text="Hyperlink"}</b> {gt text="To create a hyperlink you use this tag: &lt;a href=\"path to the site\">the title, you show the sites visitor&lt;/a>"}</li>
	<li><b>{gt text="Picture"}</b> {gt text="To include an picturein your site, you do it like this: &lt;p>&lt;img src=\"path to the picture on the server\" alt=\"The text is shown, if the picture couldn't display\"/>&lt;/p> To use a picture contact the administrantor, please. Only he can upload the picture to the server and input the right path."}</li>
	<li><b>{gt text="Style/ Layout:"}</b> {gt text="To make a better layout, you can use css tags. To include css- tags you use the style- argument: style=\"css-tag\" in a HTLM- tag. It is only recommended for user knowing what they do."}</li>
